 is advised when lithium is used with other serotonergic agents or monoamine oxidase inhibitors.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/276285/', '', 'Viloxazine', '', 1767369485);
